activity_log.text: Jill pulls you into a warm hug.
I'm so lucky to have you here.
She loosens her grip and gives you some breathing space.
I'll have to repay you somehow.
It really is nice having a man around the house.
Jill goes back to what she was doing.

You are in the kitchen.
Jill is here.
You decide to join Jill for dinner.
She vents to you about her day at work.
She seems to enjoy having someone like you to talk to.
After a moment, your phone buzzes.
Before long, you hear footsteps approaching.
You try to unleash your throbbing giant, but the zipper won't budge!
There is a tap at the door and Jill enters.
